orking visa/ 學簽，家人 VISA。 <br />\n訂機票，Book 海運家檔，收貨，出發。<br />\n<br />\n自己或者兩公婆好易計，有子女都還可以，如果有埋老人家，真係要攤出黎傾，定準啲 budget。 <br />\n<br />\n老人家學簽係唔work 只可以 spouse 同 children跟埋去，所以得返 BNO 有機會。當然好有錢又係另一種計法。<br />\n<br />\n如果連埋寵物，要提早 1 兩個月開始做，因為要計時間。<br />\n人就今日買機票聽日就走得。"},{"pid":"b37b2c1680518945a2b87665f912b1da72103c40","tid":2411514,"uid":355748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T12:06:27.000Z","msg":"問移民公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f12bd16701fef3fc859f3dd127a7ad7de21e9f1","tid":2411514,"uid":198181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a18067e2376eaff970c4255bef64b81d2e347019","tid":2411514,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T11:20:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T12:31:00.000Z","msg":"屌你老母！做支那畜牲就做！出來狗吠！屌你老母死全家！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c51413b276cbaa5842eb7063a2c1991d168bf6e","tid":2411514,"uid":336046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cda1485e59242ce3cc1fcc1981f8395e4385676","tid":2411514,"uid":268621,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a18067e2376eaff970c4255bef64b81d2e347019","tid":2411514,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T11:20:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T12:02:20.000Z","msg":"計劃洗費，如果計劃讀書計埋學費<br />\nBudget:<br />\n生活費，睇地區，租/買屋，食，水，電，車費/買車；<br />\n機票，落地暫時住宿；<br />\n保險。<br />\n<br />\n有 BNO 去英國，5年內 Post-secondary 畢業去加拿大。<br />\n以上兩樣都無，去加拿大攞學簽讀書。<br />\n<br />\n計好數，知道要幾錢，撲水，儲錢。 <br />\n<br />\n搞文件，BNOVISA / 加拿大open working visa/ 學簽，家人 VISA。 <br />\n訂機票，Book 海運家檔，收貨，出發。<